    "long_instructions": "## Travel Agent - Level 3: Multi-Shot Prompting\r\n\r\nPractice multi-shot prompting through the career of a travel agent by giving the AI a detailed and structured request that includes multiple expectations.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Try a prompt like the one below, or write a similar one that includes specific preferences and format requirements.\r\n\r\n>Recommend a family-friendly vacation destination for a family of four (two adults and two kids, ages 8 and 12) who enjoy hiking, museums, and cultural activities. Provide a sample itinerary, including accommodations, activities, and travel tips.\r\n\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how the added context improves the accuracy, relevance, and usefulness of the recommendation.",
